channel.title: Could not find process java on my restarter
channel.description: I need help and I don't know how to fix this. This is the first time this has happened to me so I need help obviously :[. My compiler is fine, it doesn't have a problem like javac is not recognized or anything like that but my restarter. When I click my voule restarter, it says could not find process java after it says restarting server. I already have a working compiler, java recognized( I have jdk6u2 and used god of ikiliki's guide also known as tico's tut). Is this normal or what should I fix...
